verbose_text: To test whether Robo1 levels could be regulated by other PY motif containing proteins, or if instead this effect is specific to the Ndfip proteins, we also performed similar experiments with Itch (a PY motif containing E3 ubiquitin ligase) and found that overexpression of Itch has no significant effect on Robo1 levels (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
